  "texts": [
    "14, who conducted an extensive study on the quality measurements of AI chatbots.",
    "The items for knowledge acquisition and knowledge application were adapted from the study by Al-Sharafi et al.",
    "The items for utilitarian value were adapted from Kim and Oh 73 and the items for satisfaction from Nguyen et al.",
    "The WOM construct items were adapted from Mishra and Shukla 75.",
    "Finally, each construct's items were measured using a seven-point Likert scale ranging from 1 (strongly disagree) to 7 (strongly agree), except for the control variables."
  ],
